com.davidsoergel.dsutils
Class PluginManager<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.davidsoergel.dsutils.PluginManager<T>

public class PluginManager<T>
extends Object

A clearinghouse for dynamically loaded plugin classes, i.e. classes that are not necessarily known at compile time but which must be identified and instantiated at runtime.

This may be redundant with other mechanisms for achieving the same thing, in particular the SubclassFinder. This class basically wraps SubclassFinder and caches the results.
